    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Pacciae Marcianae <lb n="2"/>quondam uxoris <note>sic</note> domini <lb n="3"/>nostri Imperatoris Caesaris <lb n="4"/>Luci Septimi Severi Pii Perti<lb break="no" n="5"/>nacis Augusti Arabici <lb n="6"/>Adiabenici Parthici <lb n="7"/>maximi Lepcitani Septimiani <lb n="8"/>publice ex voto <lb n="9"/>posuerunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The single original base was cut in two and reused for IRT 410 and IRT 415; the original text - half of which is on the left side of IRT 410 and half on the right side of IRT 415 - was erased.</p>
            </div>
